Because surgery's too expensive.

01:28.455 --> 01:30.695
Come on. Let's get to the
meat and potatoes of this show.

01:30.824 --> 01:33.157
What's the manliest meal
a man can fix?

01:33.226 --> 01:36.663
- Chili.
- You're darn tooting. Heidi?

01:36.730 --> 01:39.199
